public static class GuiSwingTableColumnCollection.ObjectTableColumnSizeConcrete extends ObjectTableModelColumns.ObjectTableColumnSize implements ObjectTableModelColumns.DynamicColumnFactory, Cloneable
a ObjectTableModelColumns.ObjectTableColumnSize of a concrete value. the class is also a ObjectTableModelColumns.DynamicColumnFactory, as a prototype of each size.
